text:
2.2 Example Conversation Flow

2.2.1 Initial Contact

Agent: “Hello! I’m here to help understand your business needs. Could you share your website?”
Human: “Hi, our website is www.example.com”



2.2.2 Website Analysis
{
    "scrape_data": {
        "content": "Example Inc provides retail management solutions...",
        "metadata": {
            "title": "Example Inc - Retail Solutions",
            "description": "B2B SaaS for retail management"
        }
    }
}


2.2.3 Business Understanding
{
    "analysis": {
        "business_type": "B2B SaaS",
        "target_market": "SME Retail",
        "value_proposition": "Streamlined retail management",
        "industry": "Technology/Retail"
    }
}


2.2.4 Follow-up Questions

Agent: “I notice you focus on retail. What size businesses do you typically work with?”
Human: “Mainly small to medium retailers, around 5-50 employees”
Agent: “And what’s your current customer acquisition strategy?”



2.2.5 Final Context
{
    "session_data": {
        "business_info": {
            "type": "B2B SaaS",
            "target": "SME Retail",
            "size_range": "5-50 employees"
        },
        "analysis": {
            "segmentation": "Small Business Solutions",
            "potential": "High",
            "recommended_approach": "Value-based pricing"
        }
    }
}
